<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; clear: both; min-height: 1em; vertical-align: inherit; visibility: visible; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">为了更好的了解、学习、掌握国家安全观，提高国家安全意识，经济管理学院党总支书记蔡平牵头，学生党员、发展对象、入党积极分子及各班级自主开展了对国家安全观的学习，进一步提升了对国家主权、安全及发展利益的使命责任感。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.93em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; clear: both; min-height: 1em; vertical-align: inherit; visibility: visible; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEKBXF86fP2iblG2PDSEQWP8OcTHqbaQtAXtp3nRB3AfA3Lic8qmtugqLGX1GVZDVAMwVxrXNAasQjfA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="249" height="186" style="width: 249px; height: 186px;"/></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.4352px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">开展主题班会教育，落实到日常生活，使同学了解基本的国家安全法的意识，提高遵守国家安全的自觉性，形成良好的国家安全观。</span></p>